        "content": "Dear Fellow Alumni, We are thrilled to announce the 10th Anniversary Reunion of Aggrey Memorial Old Students Association. The event will be held in June 2026. Mark your calendars and prepare for a weekend of celebration, networking, and reconnecting with old friends. More details to follow soon. Looking forward to seeing everyone!",
